  "body": "**Story**\r\nAs a user, I want to be able to read the messages seamlessly.\r\n\r\n**Current behavior**\r\nWords are cut without a specific consideration besides the size of the \"bubble\" container. That makes a message hard to read:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"368\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-08-03 a la s 10 22 13 a m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/43646113-58e703c2-970a-11e8-8793-c3d3b7a8629f.png\">\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nTo cut the words using a word-wrapping method:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"371\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-08-03 a la s 10 46 49 a m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/43646204-9fcb1e86-970a-11e8-9858-0936747eccad.png\">\r\n\r\n**Solution**\r\nImplement a word-wrapping method so if a word doesn't fit in a \"bubble\" it is pushed to the next line.\r\n",
